text.value: How often do you visit the following places?
In the last week, have you cooked one of these animals or handled their raw meat?
When you go to this place, how much time do you spend there?
Do you use any of the following substances?
What is your age in years?
A place more than 50km away (i.e. Berbera/Burco/Other country)
Do you touch any of the following animals (alive) at least once per week?
How often do you have contact with in general?
What is the name of the village, town, or settlement of the furthest place you went to last week?
Have you ever been diagnosed with any of the following illnesses by a healthcare worker?
Could you name the city/village where you contacted ?
How much time did you spend with in total?

We will now ask you to remember who you have been in contact with yesterday, between the time of waking up yesterday and the time of waking up today. A contact is someone who you met in person and with who you exchanged at least a few words.
Did you meet in Digaale, in Hargeisa, or somewhere else?
Have you received any antibiotics in the past two weeks?
Have you been feeling ill or had any of the following symptoms in the past two weeks?
Have you been within 2 meters of the following animals (alive) yesterday?
A place less than 5km away (i.e. Hargeisa)
In the last month, have you been bitten, scratched, or cut by any of these animals?
What is your primary occupation or daily activity?
A place more than 50km away (i.e. Berbera/Burco/Other country)
Confirm the date for which contacts are recorded
What is your age in months?
Age (in years) of (Always fill in years, NOT months!)
We are almost at the end of this questionnaire, but a few health related questions remain
Can you tell me your date of birth?
Is the participant a young child (<5yo)?
Could you estimate the total number of other contacts, i.e. those who you met but with who you did not speak, yesterday?
In the last month, have you killed, butchered, or feathered any of these animals?
Add a new group for each person
A place less than 5km away (i.e. Hargeisa)
Name the town or village you met with current name

We will now ask you some characteristics for each contact, such as their age and sex. We also ask whether contact was physical or not. A physical contact includes hand shaking, embracing, kissing, and also sharing a glass or utensil that is passed from mouth to mouth.
